title: Fred Gets at Like Minded Projects
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Raw, Western, Take-out
description: 3 businesses under one roof: Fred Gets offers healthy breakfast, lunch, and cold-pressed juices; Ace Cookies offers raw vegan cookies and flavored nut milks, and Coffee Supreme Roasters serves coffee drinks. The space also sells non-food things like handmade pots. Modern minimalist interior, white with lots of light and plants. Diagonally opposite Vegan Style.
